input.value:
fetch logs
| filter k8s.namespace.name == "gadget"
| filter k8s.container.name == "tester"
| parse log, " LD:node_name SPACE+ INT:progid SPACE+ LD:type SPACE+ LD:ebpf_name SPACE+ INT:pid SPACE+ LD:prog_name FLOAT:responsetime  LD:time_format SPACE+ INT:cout SPACE+ FLOAT:memory_usage WORD:format SPACE+ INT:map_count"
| fieldsAdd cpu_time=duration(responsetime,time_format) 
| filter isNotNull(memory_usage)
| filter responsetime > 0

grail.canonicalQuery:
fetch logs
| filter k8s.namespace.name == "gadget"
| filter k8s.container.name == "tester"
| parse log, " LD:node_name SPACE+ INT:progid SPACE+ LD:type SPACE+ LD:ebpf_name SPACE+ INT:pid SPACE+ LD:prog_name FLOAT:responsetime  LD:time_format SPACE+ INT:cout SPACE+ FLOAT:memory_usage WORD:format SPACE+ INT:map_count"
| fieldsAdd cpu_time = duration(responsetime, time_format)
| filter isNotNull(memory_usage)
| filter responsetime > 0
